extendedInfo.description: A quick, easy to use and lightweight location-based public transportation information application. An intuitive interface returns a listing of stops with their routes and next stop time, closest to your location.The schedules are always current and since updates to the schedules are done server-side no updates to the app are needed in order to receive the most up-to-date transit information.Features- Access to all stops and routes from all supported transit agencies- Filter by agency, type (bus, rail, etc.), date, location, stop name and route information- Favorites for quick, direct access to specified stops- Complete trip mapping with timetables- Real-time alert systemCurrently Supported AgenciesU.S. //ARIZONAValley Metro (Phoenix)CALIFORNIAAC TransitBay Area Rapid Transit - reviews.title: Very nice

reviews.title: Works very well

reviews.title: Really good
reviews.comment: It\'s a really good app, but sometimes the GPS is a bit off. Other than that, it\'s great and very accurate with the times (:
reviews.author: Lauren Self

reviews.title: Good soon to be excellent!!!
reviews.comment: Pro 1. DATA PROVIDED BY ORIGINAL TRANSIT SYSTEM TO DEVELOPER=Accurate. Pro 2. Easy of use Pro 3. Favorites available Pro 4. Map locations of specific bus root.   Pro 5. GPS, or WiFi.  Con 1. No export of favorites to cloud, or internal/external memory.  Con 2. No satellite view of maps.  Con 3. No real time GPS location of transit bus in actual movement which is available on a competitors similar app.  Con 4. No system update notifications of route disturbances/etc.  Con 5. Ui could be more creative.
reviews.author: Jelani C

reviews.title: Phenomenal App!!!#

reviews.title: How-to question...
reviews.comment: Example-I\'d like to see what King County (WA) transit bus numbers go from the University of Washington to the Redmond, Wa transit station at a given date (i.e. tomorrow) and time frame (i.e. 6:00 pm to last scheduled run) and can\'t seem figure out how to do this. Help, please. Thanks.   Update: Uprated app from 4 to 5 stars because of the speedy response of the app designer.
